Prostomium short, thick, rounded to truncate on anterior margin (
Fig. 13A
); eyespots absent; nuchal organs transverse grooves on posterior lateral margin (
Fig. 13B
). Peristomium a single ring, narrower than, but about same length as, setiger 1 (
Fig. 13A
); extending ventrally to form ventral lip of mouth.

